| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2036 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3e44ca1e-2ea0-55b9-9997-1a133d6fef04"
